## Introduction **OpenAiTx** 20 languages auto-translate tool for your GitHub project readme & wiki. ## Why? 1. One-time translation using premium-grade LLM and make the result freely accessible to the open-source community. 2. Support Google/Bing multiple languages SEO search, client translate tool can't do it. 3. Free & Open Source forever. 4.
